Hyundai Tucson
Price -Rs. 18.76 - 26.97 Lakh
The Hyundai Tucson has 1 Diesel Engine and 1 Petrol Engine on offer. The Diesel engine is 1995 cc while the Petrol engine is 1999 cc. It is available with the Manual and Automatic transmission. Depending upon the variant and fuel type the Tucson has a mileage of 12.95 to 18.42 kmpl. The Tucson is a 5 seater SUV and has a length of 4475mm, width of 1850mm and a wheelbase of 2670mm.
